overview: The fifth installment of Pierre Woodman's SuperFuckers series, has all the classic Woodman touches - beautiful women, earth-shattering sex, and a superb blend of casting, vignette, and dashes of gonzo. This time, it's Ann Kiray's turn to step up and lead the way, with eight other newcumers - Brigitta, Carrie Lee, Dorothy, Jeanette, Noemie, Nicolette, Sharon Bright and Sophie Roche for an awesome female cast.
title: Superfuckers 5
